<taxonomicName authorityName="Schepman" authorityYear="1913" box="[566,717,1954,1976]" class="Gastropoda" family="Turridae" genus="Surcula" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="brachytoma">
<emphasis box="[566,717,1954,1976]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">B. brachytoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, distribution areas and types localities are figured, not the individual collection sites.
</paragraph>
