</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[519,575,1779,1800]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[584,640,1777,1800]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">A–C.</emphasis>
Holotype, MNHN 24482, Indian Ocean, SAFARI 2, sta. CP11, SL 20.7 mm. 
